{"tid":1810330,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"傳奇藝術家Syd Mead逝世 Turn A高達設計師","createTime":"2020-01-03T18:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T17:47:06.000Z","uid":85180,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7327efeed29d600c248caa7ccccaef0cfb8fd4ee","tid":1810330,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"傳奇藝術家Syd Mead逝世 Turn A高達設計師<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532265/20200101_wes_SydMead07_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532265%2F20200101_wes_SydMead07_1024.jpg&h=43c3d4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳奇設計師兼藝術家Syd Mead逝世，他曾參與不少影視科幻作品的製作，甚至是高達迷充滿討論的《Turn A Gundam》。<br />\n<br />\n傳奇設計師兼藝術家Syd Mead逝世<br />\n曾設計《Turn A Gundam》<br />\n展示未曾有的人類未來生活概念‧將Cyberpunk文化概念變成視覺藝術<br />\n藝術家Syd Mead於12月30日因淋巴癌辭世，享年 86 歲。他在描繪人類未來生活景像的影視藝術界中甚有名氣，曾參加過《Blade Runner》、《Tron》、《 Alien》、《Star Wars》等電影的製作，描繪出符合故事背景的概念插畫，由導演與劇組人員透過鏡頭及佈景實現。另一方面，他亦有參與過遊戲製作，包括：《Cyber Tank》、《Cyber Speedway》、《Aliens: Colonial Marines》、《Wing Commander: Prophecy》等作品。至於動漫類，就有《Turn A Gundam》、《YAMATO2520》等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532265/20200101_wes_SydMead01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532265%2F20200101_wes_SydMead01_600.jpg&h=69fcd3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532265/20200101_wes_SydMead02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532265%2F20200101_wes_SydMead02_600.jpg&h=1e620150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532265/20200101_wes_SydMead05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532265%2F20200101_wes_SydMead05_600.jpg&h=6afae8df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSyd Mead本名Sydney Jay Mead，1933 年出生於明尼蘇達州，1951年高中畢業後於動畫製作公司擔任動畫師，其後進入洛杉磯藝術中心學校就讀，專攻工業設計。1959 年畢業後進入福特參與概念車款的設計。1961年Syd Mead離開福特，從事工業設計師、插畫家工作，開始以未來科幻的風格聞名。1970 年成立自己的設計公司後，在歐洲開始受到注目，更與飛利浦、Volvo 汽車公司等合作、參加過超音速客機、 NASA 太空實驗室等內部設計。1970年代開始有電影製作人尋找Syd Mead合作，參與上述不少經典科幻作品製作。在他的畫筆下，以圖像形式展現了Cyberpunk文化中對未來社會的風格描述。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532265/20200101_wes_SydMead03_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532265%2F20200101_wes_SydMead03_600.JPG&h=e398c833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2530000/2532265/20200101_wes_SydMead04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2530000%2F2532265%2F20200101_wes_SydMead04_600.jpg&h=f15fa4b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"723481a551452619ecce8a1492798ec36c61eab2","tid":1810330,"uid":51753,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:06:48.000Z","msg":"而家覺得好正<br />\n(BTW 同樣係佢設計<br />\nTurn X 就一開始都好多人接受到)"},{"pid":"7cb6afe13a9f74e2ca6e5a05c465bec630d549be","tid":1810330,"uid":251945,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"大師rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜班連登仔靜係鐘意seed同00 d機"},{"pid":"7b53bd846dbafd9fa45d82cf12a36fa0f97326e3","tid":1810330,"uid":28397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"大師好對唔住 當年唔識嘢都鬧過你設計嘅 Turn A.<br />\n<br />\n十多年後某日突然間開竅 境然愛上 Turn A 嘅 設計"},{"pid":"58d43807972bfb62a91ad1f104fba623f7168f2f","tid":1810330,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"Turn A 睇完就會接受到"},{"pid":"5e4803d3d3a803ccc699260bfc13fc3b20c36e22","tid":1810330,"uid":39177,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b53bd846dbafd9fa45d82cf12a36fa0f97326e3","tid":1810330,"uid":28397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"大師好對唔住 當年唔識嘢都鬧過你設計嘅 Turn A.<br />\n<br />\n十多年後某日突然間開竅 境然愛上 Turn A 嘅 設計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"我都係,細個覺得佢設計 on9,到大左發現呢部野好型"},{"pid":"d46e7b4af890654a6198635f267a850009930877","tid":1810330,"uid":308531,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"而家普世審美觀影響得人太深<br />\n一有啲奇怪就歸類為醜<br />\n（奇怪=唔靚（？）=醜）<br />\n但只係佢哋唔識欣賞<br />\nWorld is strange"}]}